### âœ… Optional Debug Check (in SQL console)

Run this manually in your DB to confirm:

```sql
SELECT * FROM food.M_D_ORDER_ITEM WHERE order_id = <your_order_id>;
```

and then:

```sql
SELECT * FROM food.M_D_CART;
```

If nothing new appears, it confirms the insert query failed â€” meaning the column mismatch or constraint problem caused the issue.

